"# Business UI Contract

Button policy prototype for the UI Contract Editor.

Schema version: \`0.6.0\`

## Product

- System type: business-admin
- Information density: compact
- Visual tone: calm

## Design decisions

### Foundations

- colorProfileId: \`default\`
- choiceGroupLayout: \`stacked-default-with-constrained-inline\`
- brandIdentity.mark: \`#2563eb\`
